gov.sandia.cognition.collection

Class DoubleArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.cognition.collection.DoubleArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class DoubleArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
    A memory-dense, base-type double vector that permits adding new elements, altering elements, etc. Allocates a local array of double. Doubles the size as needed and copies the old values into the new, larger array.
    See Also:

        public void reserve(int size)

        Parameters:
